WEBVTT

00:02:56.164 --> 00:03:00.048
Haya, labda naweza kuwa nabeza,

00:03:00.048 --> 00:03:04.038
na maneno yote haya ni uongo,

00:03:04.038 --> 00:03:06.829
lakini uzoefu bado unaniambia

00:03:06.829 --> 00:03:09.851
kuwa mwenye kujihadhari ni mwenye hekima.

00:03:11.848 --> 00:03:15.704
Lakini kujihadhari kunakufanya usite,

00:03:15.704 --> 00:03:19.602
na ukisita umepotea,

00:03:19.602 --> 00:03:23.509
kwa hiyo chukua fursa zako

00:03:23.509 --> 00:03:25.689
na kamwe usihesabu hasara.

00:03:25.689 --> 00:03:29.739
Gari-bembea,

00:03:29.739 --> 00:03:33.197
Farasi-bembea.